  "3214870": {
    "name": "Snow Bros. Wonderland",
    "steam_appid": 3214870,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214870/extras/9ca819e53b2bb47d4ed329e7c217f045.poster.avif?t=1770803584\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214870/extras/9ca819e53b2bb47d4ed329e7c217f045.webm?t=1770803584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214870/extras/9ca819e53b2bb47d4ed329e7c217f045.mp4?t=1770803584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>冰弹与雪球</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三十多年前，《雪人兄弟》传奇系列诞生。如今，《雪人兄弟：奇幻乐园》带着全新冒险回归啦！——几十年过去了，变化可真不小！首先，画面已经从经典的2D进化成了华丽的3D等距视角。玩家手握无限冰弹，可以将怪物变成雪球，一脚踢出，瞬间击溃成群的敌人！还能连环攻击，击倒多个敌人，而你的雪球技能也将面临巨大Boss的终极考验。你有足够的“雪胆”来保卫雪之国，抵挡邪恶的阿奇奇国王吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214870/extras/b8f088d03c1c1f51ef600e6ead88b8d9.poster.avif?t=1770803584\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214870/extras/b8f088d03c1c1f51ef600e6ead88b8d9.webm?t=1770803584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214870/extras/b8f088d03c1c1f51ef600e6ead88b8d9.mp4?t=1770803584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢乐加倍再加倍</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >过去《雪人兄弟》一直是双人游戏（毕竟名字就是这么来的），这次，直接翻倍——四人同时冒险！整个游戏更加充满乐趣。毕竟，快乐要分享，四倍的快乐更是无与伦比！哦，对了，你还可以为自己的雪人角色自定义各种装备，比如帽子、护目镜、围巾等等，找到属于你的独特风格吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214870/extras/3f57e50f2209ccdc526bd0a102053d91.poster.avif?t=1770803584\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214870/extras/3f57e50f2209ccdc526bd0a102053d91.webm?t=1770803584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214870/extras/3f57e50f2209ccdc526bd0a102053d91.mp4?t=1770803584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《雪人兄弟》的历史</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自1990年第一款《雪人兄弟》发布以来，Nick和Tom两兄弟就开始了他们滚雪球、跳平台、打怪物、展开了一场拯救公主Puripuri和Puchipuchi的冒险。四年后，《雪人兄弟2：精灵冒险》作为续作发布，这款游戏古怪而充满乐趣，深受玩家喜爱。然而，在这之后，我们就再也没有看到新的正统续作——直到今天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那么，你还在等什么呢？叫上朋友，一起加入这场冰雪大冒险吧！</p>",
